To all<br><br>
Such a WEALTH OF WISDOM!  I always quoted the saying &quot;Little people talk about other people, ordinary people talk about things, but GREAT people talk about ideas.&quot;  <br><br>
You are great people, great works of art, in progress.  Anyone can &quot;sketch&quot; a two dimensional life and most do.  But, there are few Michalangelos - the pain, frustration, determination and soul that it takes is beyond most.  All great works take &quot;blood, sweat and tears&quot;, each &quot;failure&quot; (no matter how large) adds to the richness to the painting, but NEVER lose sight of the magnitude of your pursuit. <br><br>
ANNE
